{"tid":297393,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"想養龍貓，邊度買抵屌","createTime":"2017-06-25T12:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T01:00:32.000Z","uid":47978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"390dafbfb521a16dc66868e15d21081049c6d5c8","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T12:06:03.000Z","msg":"屋企 糧食 設備果啲搵好晒<br />\n有冇巴絲知邊度有唔貴既龍貓賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0164afb5a1331ef9d747caf4a5fa3f4df6db5d1a","tid":297393,"uid":11034,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"標準答案：領養"},{"pid":"3af4cb48aa0443167e930e8b9fcc798308846d8c","tid":297393,"uid":76908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T13:56:39.000Z","msg":"好似龍貓唔好單獨養？<br />\n姐係唔好單單養一隻"},{"pid":"7d54be67d71f137f97a177005cb4a405118d6d34","tid":297393,"uid":6931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T15:43:04.000Z","msg":"出街執"},{"pid":"6915ab9ccff16a50654fb76b6972ae969cfd560e","tid":297393,"uid":3146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T18:14:07.000Z","msg":"淘寶"},{"pid":"943fc294d099fbbc999091c8191c84a113174305","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案：領養</blockquote><br />\n愛協好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a15ef01b01d0b8da3f4e7675938c6761d25ba46","tid":297393,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企 糧食 設備果啲搵好晒<br />\n有冇巴絲知邊度有唔貴既龍貓賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平既金魚街啲地鋪千幾二千都有，不過健康同血統無乜保證<br />\n利申買左隻地鋪龍貓，好似2千蚊，依家2歲幾除左磅數輕少少之外無健康問題"},{"pid":"d86fb9b5b830bf52c731322fc7e43100d55104d8","tid":297393,"uid":124114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T15:47:43.000Z","msg":"個FD以前養過一隻好惡會咬人,會流血<br />\n又唔比人抱,呢D真係睇手神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9491efa0dafacd9585c21d4d991f86ceb0376702","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:09:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屋企 糧食 設備果啲搵好晒<br />\n有冇巴絲知邊度有唔貴既龍貓賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n平既金魚街啲地鋪千幾二千都有，不過健康同血統無乜保證<br />\n利申買左隻地鋪龍貓，好似2千蚊，依家2歲幾除左磅數輕少少之外無健康問題</blockquote><br />\n千幾二千<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇親都六千以上<br />\n<br />\n邊間鋪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1303b4def2dde51408d2f7f0d070f94b0bc0b3","tid":297393,"uid":83759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上"},{"pid":"9656dc09830b449e39ab0a2080561ccbe480ac8d","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上</blockquote><br />\n地鋪有啲6千幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知邊度平 太貴買完比屋企人屌"},{"pid":"cba6756926aa068efb8635ec1888d2b6d61ee017","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T15:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013c838663b4ff669d65ea46b498d70dcc234302","tid":297393,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T00:01:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMini zoo貴到仆街，無4,5千都埋唔到單<br />\n我唔記得個鋪名，但係有2,3間都會有呢個價，不過選擇唔多"},{"pid":"9a0f6a05810b129a34c55dc769c95eab510b8e15","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T02:01:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMini zoo貴到仆街，無4,5千都埋唔到單<br />\n我唔記得個鋪名，但係有2,3間都會有呢個價，不過選擇唔多</blockquote><br />\n我暫時未見到金魚街地鋪有平既龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway 唔該曬"},{"pid":"d5feae5eda37ba8420da312ca551f606a114a058","tid":297393,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>旺角樓上鋪有間叫MINIZOO <br />\n有幾種色 又分老豆老母後代血統點樣點樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n印象中都要2千以上</blockquote><br />\n好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMini zoo貴到仆街，無4,5千都埋唔到單<br />\n我唔記得個鋪名，但係有2,3間都會有呢個價，不過選擇唔多</blockquote><br />\n我暫時未見到金魚街地鋪有平既龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway 唔該曬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早2,3個月去買野都仲見到，有無睇狗仔粉斜對面果間？我都係果間買，不過唔好聽佢教點養，伏到仆街"},{"pid":"532bc6cc12a430911a9e872c60abf94abb1ef4c2","tid":297393,"uid":100936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T03:27:09.000Z","msg":"北角有間龍X仔專門店都有賣龍貓<br />\n我記得係1500起 你有時間可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過啲服務就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d40044abde1dc3193636a72838525f7aea6a94c","tid":297393,"uid":50515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"屋企無貓就領養<br />\n有就唔好領養啦"},{"pid":"edefd31e4c80213d2dd558fdc6a266697a442446","tid":297393,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T18:26:59.000Z","msg":"龍貓其實痴唔痴人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5293b9fa823614652733c092412d81ae27c7856","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北角有間龍X仔專門店都有賣龍貓<br />\n我記得係1500起 你有時間可以去睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過啲服務就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭先係果度買完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時間交流下"},{"pid":"6f0e116a06366df1d62ece57a4b02f592c879583","tid":297393,"uid":47978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T06:48:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>龍貓其實痴唔痴人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴 我頭先揀果陣 申隻手都係咁咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342dc3d2038a28c7fc8bd7881f7fa8fbf4df72a4","tid":297393,"uid":6031,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"愛協都話煩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfe1730f7fbffcb33c8aabc8f37a7515931213af","tid":297393,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T11:06:16.000Z","msg":"巴打揀左咩色啊？<br />\n夏天小心啲溫度問題，龍貓唔係幾熱得<br />\n最後求圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f432537578e05c08059f50e940ee1e70bc72d730","tid":297393,"uid":104333,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:22:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>龍貓其實痴唔痴人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴 我頭先揀果陣 申隻手都係咁咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n似係憎你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我掙扎緊養貓定龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677ef10fc8fb5ac43a6b5c02e31cb2759a601f0b","tid":297393,"uid":34177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T16:36:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍貓其實痴唔痴人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴 我頭先揀果陣 申隻手都係咁咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n似係憎你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我掙扎緊養貓定龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n養龍貓你夏天要成日開風扇冷氣比佢喎<br />\n佢地毛厚好怕熱<br />\n平時屋企成日開冷氣？<br />\n<br />\n申手會咬你好正常 <br />\n新氣味既野咪咬下睇下食唔食得 <br />\n<br />\n痴人呢樣未必隻隻一樣<br />\n我兩隻龍貓 痴人都係一時時<br />\n有野食就好痴你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你考慮緊d咩問題去揀貓定龍貓？<br />\n等我解答你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9854543ea8f3ed252e594c926b3817d17d7f1ade","tid":297393,"uid":93864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T17:41:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>龍貓其實痴唔痴人架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n痴 我頭先揀果陣 申隻手都係咁咬我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n似係憎你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我掙扎緊養貓定龍貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/014041_1cb77c6b400654c1cc4eac3b22d2dc07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F014041_1cb77c6b400654c1cc4eac3b22d2dc07.jpg&h=9bb6e590&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/014042_a9dc57501470ebf4ba3aab0536e8e871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F014042_a9dc57501470ebf4ba3aab0536e8e871.jpg&h=4afef881&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/16/014043_a9dc57501470ebf4ba3aab0536e8e871.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F16%2F014043_a9dc57501470ebf4ba3aab0536e8e871.jpg&h=a2e96820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n毒下你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}